{"id": 1333, "genre": 1001, "title": "今年别人给你戴的“帽子”，你想摘一摘吗？", "description": "你们这都是偏见，我要为自己洗白！（题图来自：Kathrin Honesta）", "record_count": 2510, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20161116181419qANO70K4tgup5yFC.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-11-18T03:00:40Z", "options": [{"id": 134912, "content": "长得帅穿衣服喜欢中性风不代表我是拉拉…", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216775}, {"id": 135168, "content": "我不是没有脾气 只是不表现出来", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 839285}, {"id": 134913, "content": "只是装个样。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 66516}, {"id": 134914, "content": "只是装个样子而已。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 66516}, {"id": 134915, "content": "我热情地推荐，介绍什么给你，我并不是另有所图，只是单纯的分享罢了，可你竟然还认为我有精神疾病???", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 759638}, {"id": 135171, "content": "我不是一个工作特别努力的人，我只是觉得我不努力的干不好意思拿这份工资", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 839292}, {"id": 134916, "content": "我可以当空姐。我有能力考上我想要的研究生。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 84116}, {"id": 135172, "content": "我喜欢你，不是给你笑话的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 836060}, {"id": 134917, "content": "工作狂", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 805902}, {"id": 134918, "content": "为什么要摘下来？摘下来不就是承认了。做自己需要别人来评价嘛？", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 833043}, {"id": 135174, "content": "我是脾气好 那只是素质不代表别的什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 509501}, {"id": 134919, "content": "烦烦烦烦烦烦烦烦烦烦烦烦烦烦烦烦烦烦", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 766422}, {"id": 134920, "content": "不是我脸上没表情就是冷漠，不近人情，我是真的不知道该有什么表情，难道一直笑？我不是二哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 273397}, {"id": 138760, "content": "你只认识今天的我，或者某个小事的我\n而我已经认识自己21年了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 852712}, {"id": 134921, "content": "想摘，但是由不得我。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 798545}, {"id": 134922, "content": "我沉默不是因为我不在乎", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 176483}, {"id": 138250, "content": "我送他一打 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 776389}, {"id": 134923, "content": "你说什么 我听不清 ……", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 830035}, {"id": 135179, "content": "我不是花花公子", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 633635}, {"id": 134924, "content": "我不傻不聋不瞎\n有些事情不说不代表我不知道\n你也不傻不聋不瞎\n所以别从别人说的来\n了解我\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 830974}, {"id": 135180, "content": "好好爱家人 比什么都来得实在", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 726111}, {"id": 135181, "content": "我是努力工作，但不代表我会为任何人做任何事，其中更多的杂事琐事！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 839311}, {"id": 134926, "content": "没有主见", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 494480}, {"id": 134927, "content": "不是话中带脏就是低俗。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 819786}, {"id": 135183, "content": "忍耐是有限度的，还没爆发，说明我的修养完爆那个粗鄙的“boss”……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 838381}, {"id": 134928, "content": "心情，就像内裤，\n你得有，但不必逢人就证明你有。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 838062}, {"id": 134929, "content": "我不烦你是为了让你别来烦我", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 727191}, {"id": 135185, "content": "无力的辩解就像坐实了某件事;有力的辩解又像是在表明你脆弱的内心？所以大部分时候我保持沉默。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 839325}, {"id": 135186, "content": "没脾气", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 839328}, {"id": 135187, "content": "我不说你，是因为我尊重你", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 839332}, {"id": 143891, "content": "反正她都以为我啥都不懂不知道无感那我就做成那样让她一直以为下去好了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 867018}, {"id": 135188, "content": "学霸，大神，大佬，膜", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 697669}, {"id": 134933, "content": "无所谓，你高兴就好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 835237}, {"id": 134934, "content": "我追星但不是每天对着手机舔屏，从不在网上骂人，没有整天幻想嫁给偶像，心智是成年人的懂判断，脑子好好的没残。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 773654}, {"id": 135190, "content": "有时候傻傻的，并不代表我什么都看不懂", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 839384}, {"id": 134936, "content": "紧它吧。酸酸甜甜", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 838083}, {"id": 134937, "content": "去你的人好，只是懒得搭理", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 838070}, {"id": 134938, "content": "我也不是一点不在乎，但你要我说出来，那我真的其实一点都不在乎。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 800895}, {"id": 135450, "content": "我学物理，但是我也是个经常少女心爆棚的妹子，谢谢", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 826621}, {"id": 134939, "content": "有些时候，遇到熟识的人不是不想打招呼，是怕突然的开口，打破了一切安静的美好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 243611}, {"id": 135963, "content": "不要把每个人都看成不如自己的傻子，其实你才是最需要补脑的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 834971}, {"id": 136731, "content": "用你的职位来假设你的性格。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 788952}, {"id": 135453, "content": "只是懒得点破罢了，若真要斗一斗，t有谁能挡我？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 733586}, {"id": 134942, "content": "我每天嘻嘻哈哈，不是我傻。我每天呵呵一笑，只是我不去争。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 838077}, {"id": 134943, "content": "表面装傻，不在乎，其实我比谁都清楚", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 826475}, {"id": 134944, "content": "我的想法，少有人懂。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 704634}, {"id": 136992, "content": "“别一天到晚只知道学习”\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668508}, {"id": 134946, "content": "喜欢了就是喜欢了，没有性别区分，不喜欢就是不喜欢，没有为什么。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 838128}, {"id": 135202, "content": "你觉得我不好大概是因为我不喜欢你吧，人总是喜欢用自己的三观看待别人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 764668}, {"id": 150562, "content": "我不是心大，只是在忍受你们", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 600246}]}